Package: MetaPoly
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Massimo", "Bourquin", , "massimo.bourquin@epfl.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4187-7485"))
Description: The MetaPoly aims at describing from a population genomic point of view metagenomics data. For this, several methods are developed to analyse the occurrence of polymorphism, the allele frequencies variations, along with positive selection inferences.
